GENEROUS couple Jean and Alastair Scott paid for a toilet block in Africa while buying a new bathroom for their home. Couple help flush poverty GENEROUS couple Jean and Alastair Scott paid for a toilet block in Africa while buying a new bathroom for their home.They donated through charity Toilet Twinning, which aims to reduce the number of people across the world who do not have access to safe and sanitary conditions.Nearly one in five child deaths each year is due to diarrhoea. 